veral days after the media reported that they had left the most dynamic and popular female athlete in the world today, Caitlin Clark, off of their Olympic roster.\", \"from\": 795, \"to\": 1136, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The league broke the news after Caitlin Clark drained seven 3-point shots, scored 30 points, led in assists, and filled a 20,000-seat arena in Washington, DC, the night before the news broke.\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1329, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1170, \"end\": 1183, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caitlin_Clark\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Caitlin Clark\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caitlin_Clark\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caitlin_Clark\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Clark put on a clinic.\", \"from\": 1330, \"to\": 1352, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It did not matter.\", \"from\": 1353, \"to\": 1371, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Clark broke all of the attendance records in the first half of the season - It did not matter.Clark led the league in 3-point shots when they picked the Olympic team - It did not matter.Clark was bringing in MILLIONS of new fans to the league for the first time ever - It did not matter.Clark is the most exciting player in basketball today - It did not matter.\", \"from\": 1373, \"to\": 1734, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This was not enough for these angry women to put Clark on the Olympic team where she belonged.\", \"from\": 1736, \"to\": 1830, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The world was waiting for Caitlin Clark to play in the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 1832, \"to\": 1902, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1858, \"end\": 1871, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caitlin_Clark\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Caitlin Clark\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caitlin_Clark\